No. 09-669. Anthony DiPlacido, Petitioner v. Commodity Futures Trading Commission. 559 U.S. 1025, 130 S. Ct. 1883,

176 L. Ed. 2d 399,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2461. March 22, 2010.
